            div.c-button__center
              a(href="https://www.segasammy.co.jp/english/pr/corp/history/", target="_blank").c-button__more-history.c-button__blank.u-mg-center
                |See more details about 
                br
                |History of SEGA SAMMY Group

            - 
              var navigatorObject = {
                text: "Business",
                rootClass: "c-navigator__02",
                imgPath: `${config.assets_link}` + "images/02_mv.png",
                alt: "ALIYAN",
